profile: At Steam Dry Canada, our customers are our business. Whether it is our carpet, upholstery, area rug, furnace and duct cleaning, indoor air quality division or the flood rescue division, we strive to give our customers superior, detailed and precise results. Our service technicians will provide these superior services with integrity and sincere customer service. We don't send salespeople into our customers homes, we send qualified technicians that are focused on meeting and exceeding our customers expectations. We want to give our customers the most enjoyable in-home service that they have ever received and we are not satisfied until our customers are satisfied, guaranteed.

profile:
Pure Fresh Furnace & Duct Cleaning Inc. is a local Family Owned business serving Edmonton & surrounding areas. Your satisfaction is very important to us and we stand behind our work with your Happiness and Satisfaction Guaranteed. We are a group of Engineers, Specialists and Technicians who can offer excellent HVAC cleaning services to the city Edmonton for Residential and Commercial businesses. Our expert furnace cleaning services are prompt and affordable. Our main interest is keeping the air quality in your premise clean and healthy. Our Corporate Vision is: “TO BE THE PREMIER IN FURNACE/DUCT CLEANING & ENERGY COMPANY IN ALBERTA, MOST ADMIRED FOR ITS EXCELLENCE, SERVICE AND RELIABLE SUPPORT”.

We're social here:
https://www.facebook.com/PureFreshFurnace
https://www.instagram.com/purefreshfurnacecleaning/
services:
We are happy to serve you and make you our most satisfied customer. Our services includes (but not limited to);
Ducting Systems Cleaning
Furnace Blower/Fan Coil/Heat Exchanger Cleaning and Detailing
Air Conditioning Coil cleaning
Central Vacuum System Cleaning
Dryer Vent Cleaning (internal/external)
Dryer Vent Hose Replacement
HRV/ERV cleaning
Hot Water Tank Vent cleaning
Humidifier Cleaning, Servicing and New Design & Installation
Pet Free Service package for clients who have allergies to pet hairs and also to Religious Establishments
FREE sanitization of your vents & ducts, vacuuming of your home at affected areas
FREE Multi Point inspection of your HVAC system
Filter Subscription & Annual Maintenance Program, AND MORE…
